{
  "stem": "19969.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from there I was assigned to the 45th Infantry Division, which was a National Guard Division, which had been mobilized in September of 1940.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they were considerably short of personnel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was assigned to the 45th Infantry Division while I was at Fort Sill, Oklahoma.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and specifically, I was assigned to the 157th Infantry Regiment, which is one of the regiments of the 45th Division.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that was the beginning of that one-year assignment, presumably.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Turned out to be over five years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because before my year was up, Pearl Harbor came along.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course, then the general mobilization started.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so I spent five years with that regiment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was a student at the Infantry School at Fort Benning, Georgia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] This was a school conducted by the Army for infantry officers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- ran about three months, four months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I happened to be a student there at the time of Pearl Harbor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my year was going to be up the following month.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I thought I was going to be getting out of the Army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Instead, what I got-- I remember that Sunday morning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We got the news by radio-- that was before TV-- that the Japs had hit Pearl Harbor.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we all knew that we weren't going to get out in a year.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we geared up, then, for wartime service.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I returned to my unit, which was on Camp Barkelet, Texas.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from there on, we went to various places in the United States and were finally sent to North Africa in June of 1943.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At that time, I was a captain.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
